Parameters:
name - armor name
description - armor description
numItem - number of objects for this armor
symbol - character that will be displayed on map for this armor
hp - how much will be added to player hp
mana - how much will be added to player mana
strength - how much will be added to player strength
intelligence - how much will be added to player intelligence
dexterity - how much will be added to player dexterity
